Attrition Overview

Total number of employees.

Total attrition count and attrition rate (% who left).

Attrition by department/job role.

SELECT 
    COUNT(*) AS TotalEmployees,
    SUM(CASE WHEN Attrition = 'Yes' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS EmployeesLeft,
    CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN Attrition = 'Yes' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 100.0 / COUNT(*) AS DECIMAL(5,2)) AS AttritionRate
FROM Employment_Attribute;
